{"id":185,"parent_id":0,"book_id":8,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":185,"title":"Benjamin","subtitle":"","short_title":"Benjamin","uri":"/scriptures/bd/benjamin","content":[["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/benjamin.t1","order":".000.496"},[".title","Benjamin"],["div",{"id":"p1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/benjamin.p1","order":".000.497"},["i","Son of the right hand."],"(1) Son of Jacob and Rachel; his birth,",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/35.18"},"Gen. 35:18"],"; how brought to Egypt and treated by Joseph,",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/42?span=42-45"},"Gen. 42–45"],"; blessing of, by Jacob,",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.27"},"49:27"],"; by Moses,",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/33.12"},"Deut. 33:12"],"; border and cities,",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/18.11-28"},"Josh. 18:11–28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/21.4,17"},"21:4, 17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/1.21"},"Judg. 1:21"],". The Benjamites were a warlike race and did great service in resisting the Philistine oppression. The tribe provided the first king in the person of Saul (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/9.1-2"},"1 Sam. 9:1–2"],"). At the division of the kingdom Benjamin joined the northern tribes (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/12.21"},"1 Kgs. 12:21"],"), but the nearness to Jerusalem seems to have caused Benjamin gradually to become part of the kingdom of Judah. The most distinguished Benjamite was the Apostle Paul (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.1"},"Rom. 11:1"],")."],["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/scriptures/bd/benjamin.p2","order":".000.498"},"(2)",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/7.10"},"1 Chr. 7:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/scriptures/bd/benjamin.p3","order":".000.499"},"(3)",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/10.32"},"Ezra 10:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/3.23"},"Neh. 3:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/12.34"},"12:34"],"."]]],"refs":null}
